  "title": "SECRETARY - BOARD MEMBER OFFICE (SGX LISTED FIRM)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- Salary: Up to $6,500</strong><br /><strong>- SGX Listed Investment firm</strong><br /><strong>- Working location: walking distance from Orchard MRT</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide admin & secretarial support to the a Senior Director whom is the Board Member of several Listed Companies</p></li><li><p>Coordinate appointments and calendar management</p></li><li><p>Handling of confidential-related matters.</p></li><li><p>Handling email correspondences</p></li><li><p>Manage Drivers and their daily work schedules</p></li><li><p>Sourcing of corporate/ festive gifts and managing the delivery schedules</p></li><li><p>Sourcing and purchase of office equipment and office supplies</p></li><li><p>Maintain office administrative files; electronic or physical, ensuring easy retrieval and accessibility<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least Private Secretarial qualification or GCE ‘A’ Level</p></li><li><p>At least 5 years of secretarial relevant work experience in supporting senior management</p></li><li><p>Secretary experience in support Board Member of SGX listed company</p></li><li><p>Candidate with relevant experience in government agencies will have advantage</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Chinese to liaise with Chinese speaking counterparts<br /></p></li></ul><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed Word format to<br /></p><p><a href=\"mailto:roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>roy.yeo@peopleprofilers.com</strong></a></p><p><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified<br />People Profilers Pte Ltd<br />50 Raffles Place, #19-12, Singapore Land Tower, Singapore 048623<br />EA License Number:  02C4944<br />Registration Number: R1217882<br />Posting Personnel: Yeo Yi Rong<br />Tel: <a href=\"tel:6950%209757\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6950 9757</strong></a></p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
